  m_text: "I'm <color=#FFFFFFFF>Kang</color>, ex-programmer at <color=#FFFFFFFF>Fntastic</color>.
    Core gameplay mechanics are my bread and butter, but I'm comfortable across the
    full dev stack \u2014 Unity is my weapon of choice.\n\nThis project exists to
    show what I can actually do. Commercial work kept me too busy for side projects,
    and the projects we shipped at <color=#FFFFFFFF>Fntastic</color> got taken down
    shortly after release \u2014 so they only exist as a line of text in my portfolio."
